<p><b>Apocalyptica</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Finland" title="Finland">Finnish</a> <a href="/wiki/Cello_rock" title="Cello rock">cello metal</a> band, composed of classically trained <a href="/wiki/Cellists" title="Cellists" class="mw-redirect">cellists</a> and, since 2005, a drummer. Three of the cellists are graduates of the <a href="/wiki/Sibelius_Academy" title="Sibelius Academy">Sibelius Academy</a> in <a href="/wiki/Helsinki" title="Helsinki">Helsinki</a>, <a href="/wiki/Finland" title="Finland">Finland</a>. Their music features elements from <a href="/wiki/Classical_music" title="Classical music">classical music</a>, <a href="/wiki/Neo-classical_metal" title="Neo-classical metal">neo-classical metal</a>,<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> <a href="/wiki/Thrash_metal" title="Thrash metal">thrash metal</a>, and <a href="/wiki/Symphonic_metal" title="Symphonic metal">symphonic metal</a>.</p>
